ection. The name has been in regular use in England since the 16th century.  See also  Milo   and   Myles ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1355923,"age":7,"year":"1167","julianDay":2147298,"description":"Arrival of Normans at Baginbun in Co. Wexford thus started 800 year struggle between English and Irish.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"John Miles de Courcy was born about 1160, in Dublin, Ireland as the son of John Earl of Ulster de Courcy. He had at least 3 sons. He died in 1208, in Ireland, at the age of 49."},"et":{"Abt 1160–1208":"umbes 1160–1208","1160–1208":"1160–1208","1182–1244":"1182–1244","1185–1223":"1185–1223","–1251":"–1251","1134–1210":"1134–1210","1223":"1223","1167":"1167","1134":"1134","1244":"1244","1210":"1210","1251":"1251","1185":"1185","Abt 1160":"umbes 1160","1182":"1182","1160":"1160","1208":"1208","Dublin, Ireland":"Dublin, Iirimaa","Ireland":"Iirimaa"},"fi":{"Abt 1160–1208":"noin 1160–1208","1160–1208":"1160–1208","1182–1244":"1182–1244","1185–1223":"1185–1223","–1251":"–1251","1134–1210":"1134–1210","1223":"1223","1167":"1167","1134":"1134","1244":"1244","1210":"1210","1251":"1251","1185":"1185","Abt 1160":"noin 1160","1182":"1182","1160":"1160","1208":"1208","Dublin, Ireland":"Dublin, Irlanti","Ireland":"Irlanti"},"fr":{"Abt 1160–1208":"environ 1160–1208","1160–1208":"1160–1208","1182–1244":"1182–1244","1185–1223":"1185–1223","–1251":"–1251","1134–1210":"1134–1210","1223":"1223","1167":"1167","1134":"1134","1244":"1244","1210":"1210","1251":"1251","1185":"1185","Abt 1160":"environ 1160","1182":"1182","1160":"1160","1208":"1208","Dublin, Ireland":"Dublin, Irlande","Ireland":"Irlande","lifeSummary":"John Miles de Courcy est né environ 1160, à Dublin, Irlande, fils de John Earl of Ulster de Courcy. Il a eu au moins 3 fils. Il est décédé en 1208, à Irlande, à l’âge de 49 ans."},"de":{"Abt 1160–1208":"um 1160–1208","1160–1208":"1160–1208","1182–1244":"1182–1244","1185–1223":"1185–1223","–1251":"–1251","1134–1210":"1134–1210